{"tid":1011683,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人生低潮期獲Eason千嬅力撐 Edison今不認朋友","createTime":"2019-02-07T03:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T04:07:33.000Z","uid":147522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd99a8ef27441b8857522b757aa1dd83031ba1d","tid":1011683,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5UyQyz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5UyQyz.png&h=d2c7319a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳冠希（Edison）對網民提出好友陳奕迅（Eason）和契姐楊千嬅現在都轉向支持余文樂的品牌，Edison即發火謂二人不是他的朋友。其實於2008年Edison宣佈退出香港娛樂圈後，在他最低潮時期，Eason與千嬅仍有跟他聯絡及力撐他。<br />\n<br />\n2009年，Eason在內地受訪，謂於美國舉行巡迴演唱會期間在三藩市跟Edison見過面，更謂對方訴說很掛念香港，一個人在外國生活很寂寞，並謂經常有通電話聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n至於契姐楊千嬅一直力撐Edison，同年陳父申請破產，千嬅被問會否經濟上支持Edison？她說幫到一定幫，但強調Edison是個自力更生的人，並透露在msn保持聯絡。"},{"pid":"787c145d43d827195164ccd234d75d56d733bb07","tid":1011683,"uid":5652,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"佢地單方面話有聯絡姐 <br />\nEdc同檸檬反面後 單春同佢仲係咪fd都成問題啦"},{"pid":"f875c158d3eb668a278b2ec4c620cdaae6de4378","tid":1011683,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a46dceb2e4db728ce3777c4b96c1dc524a5a6a","tid":1011683,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:55:28.000Z","msg":"不如調轉問娛樂圈有邊個係陳冠希朋友"},{"pid":"5ffd1500a38035d5f8dc9f7e3a9dbb9a8565a47a","tid":1011683,"uid":84128,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d2a46dceb2e4db728ce3777c4b96c1dc524a5a6a","tid":1011683,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:55:28.000Z","msg":"不如調轉問娛樂圈有邊個係陳冠希朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"但市民大眾都是陳冠希朋友"},{"pid":"ca4de77987f7d6c2ae911d084bbfbfb589826d81","tid":1011683,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2a46dceb2